Description:
    Generate GraphQL interfaces for a given model, such as a top-level collection, getter by slug, and resolver.

Example:
    bin/rails generate model_interface SomeModel

    This will create:
        app/graphql/types/some_model_order_type.rb
        app/graphql/types/some_model_type.rb
        app/services/resolvers/ordered_as_some_model.rb
        app/services/resolvers/some_model_resolver.rb
        spec/requests/graphql/query/some_model_spec.rb
        spec/requests/graphql/query/some_models_spec.rb
